{"tid":1478680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有兩日，我有一計，誠邀各位手足入黎","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:33:19.000Z","uid":95541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2de71c6a9d5d61b2ef801e96a7b525daaa8e527e","tid":1478680,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"我地嘅宣傳不外乎係連儂牆、傳單、airdrop，通通都係視覺上的宣傳，點解我地唔突破視覺，向聽覺出發，其實好簡單，攞起部電話，自己錄一段錄音，簡單到一句「818維園見」就已經有宣傳效果。<br />\n不過請切記，   <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好係咁loop，否則有反效果</span><br />\n<br />\n甚至只要自己上YouTube 睇一段關於五大訴求的片段、一啲感動到自己的片段，用較大的音量去播就令人知道。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住，呢招我地要喺交通工具尤其地鐵內用</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">化文字為聲音行動，正式展開！我自己聽日就出去招地鐵嗰陣播攪炒巴段演講，希望見到同路人</span>"},{"pid":"a33911ce279275ec8078da172a88ff8476208a61","tid":1478680,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25cc04d517de6ff319c2375c17bf5bcf050dd13e","tid":1478680,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"推，多啲人一齊做"},{"pid":"4c09b84562a73bdb1f4702417995f6c5153eea1e","tid":1478680,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6b50197e2b8a14d22d27ec6247d8ad1b69e8872","tid":1478680,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47dde31506965533c5b6a2c606e43343b3b070a4","tid":1478680,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abe9de5404120c4abcefad61b18c7b37ef619fec","tid":1478680,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}